          <p class="u-pushBottom">
           <b>
            Graphic Contest Brief
           </b>
           <span class="u-block">
            We want you to have a bit of fun with design, so we've launched this contest to 'hipsterize' Disney characters. Grab high-res photos of Disney characters, and accessorize and hipsterize them! Have fun with graphics, illustrations, and photoshop to make them the most convincing hipster out there! Most importantly, have fun!
            <br/>
            <br/>
            You can use any Disney character - Ariel from Little Mermaid, Jasmine and Aladdin, Cinderella, Tinker Bell, Hercules, Pocahontas, Mulan, Snow White, Mini and Mickey Mouse, Pinocchio, Tarzan, Woody and Buzz Lightyear.
            <br/>
            <br/>
            Think of hand-me-down skinny jeans, thick framed glasses, vintage cameras, beards, maroon beanies, Dr. Martens, fixed-gear bicycles and non-descript tattoos. If that does not get your creative juices flowing, this informative graphic on the evolution of the hipster by Hipster Approved will surely help you out. (File attached)
            <br/>
            <br/>
            The winner will be chosen based on how much they make us laugh, and how convincing the hipster conversion of the Disney character is!
            <br/>
           </span>
          </p>
